			<h2><a href="/blog/ft-generative-ai-valuation/">Generative AI: hype not hyperintelligence is lifting values</a></h2>
			<h3><span title="Where I published this post from">London</span> | Published <time>15 November 2023</time> in <a href="/categories/ai">AI</a> | 10 minute read | <a href="https://x.com/intent/tweet?text=Generative%20AI%3a%20hype%20not%20hyperintelligence%20is%20lifting%20values&url=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fft-generative-ai-valuation%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/twitter-x.svg" alt="Share this post on X" title="Share this post on X" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/cws/share?url=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fft-generative-ai-valuation%2f&xdOrigin=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2f&xd_origin_host=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2f" target="_blank"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/linkedin.svg" alt="Share this post on LinkedIn" title="Share this post on LinkedIn" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:?subject=Have a read&body=https%3a%2f%2fmariothomas.com%2fblog%2fft-generative-ai-valuation%2f"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/envelope.svg" alt="Share this post by Email" title="Share this post by Email" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://mariothomas.com/blog/ft-generative-ai-valuation/" onclick="copyURL('copyit'); return false;" id="copyit"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/link.svg" alt="Copy the Permalink to this post" title="Copy the Permalink to this post" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.ft.com/content/26d9f37b-bf22-4662-9fc8-1a1ae50011f3" target="_blank" title="Follow this link to read the article on FT.com"><img height="16" width="16" src="/img/box-arrow-up-right.svg" alt="" /></a></h3>
		</header>

		
		
		<p>Interesting read (pay-walled) <a href="https://www.ft.com/content/26d9f37b-bf22-4662-9fc8-1a1ae50011f3">in the FT</a> on what&rsquo;s driving valuations in the generative AI space. The key to the adoption of any technology is finding the right investment case and quickly demonstrating proof of value. Generative AI is no different.</p>
		
